text: Jonathan Robert McHenry (19 October 1919 – 21 January 2003) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy and Geelong in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1919 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Geelong Football Club players
